== 大眾文化中的伽勒撞擊坑 ==
伽勒撞擊坑在[[艾倫·摩爾|艾倫·摩爾]]（Alan Moore）和[[大衛·吉布斯|大衛·吉布斯]]（Dave Gibbons）的漫畫《[[守護者_(漫畫)|守護者]]》（Watchmen）中出現；2009年該漫畫改編成的[[守護者_(電影)|同名電影]]上映<ref>{{cite news | url = http://archives.chicagotribune.com/2009/mar/01/entertainment/chi-0301-watchmenmar01 | title = 'Watchmen': Your guide to watching the big screen adaptation of the comic book | date = February 27, 2009 | publisher = [[Chicago_Tribune|Chicago Tribune]] | author = Web Behrens | accessdate = 2010-05-01 | archive-date = 2009-05-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090505200112/http://archives.chicagotribune.com/2009/mar/01/entertainment/chi-0301-watchmenmar01 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 另一個「笑臉撞擊坑」 ==
2008年1月28日，[[火星偵察軌道器|火星偵察軌道器]]的影像中發現另一個「笑臉撞擊坑」。直徑比伽勒撞擊坑小，位於[[涅瑞達山脈|涅瑞達山脈]]（Nereidum Montes），座標45.1°S, 55.0°W<ref>[http://www.planetary.org/blog/article/00001314/ Have a happy day on Mars] {{Wayback|url=http://www.planetary.org/blog/article/00001314/ |date=20100421201318 }} , [[行星學會|The Planetary Society]] Blog, Feb. 1, 2008</ref>。

